cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a novel graph-based approach for semi-supervised learning using neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach is applied to computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) in the experiments. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of regularization techniques (cs.NE) in the proposed method. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
